== '''UBUZIMA BWITE''' ==
'''Dr Karekezi Claire''' (wavutse 1983) ni inzobere (Docteur) yize iby'imikorere y'[[ubwonko]], kubaga ubwonko ndetse no kuvura indwara zibwibasira n'imitsi ikorana nabwo,<ref>https://rw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claire_Karekezi?veaction=edit</ref>  ni umwe muri bacye mu banyarwanda  wabashije kwiga kubaga [[ubwonko]], ndetse akaba yarahawe n'ibihembo bitandukanye.

== AMASHURI YIZE ==
'''Dr Karekezi Claire''' ( yavukiye i [[Perefegitura ya Butare|Butare]]) ariko yaje kwiga mu [[umujyi wa Kigali]] aho amashuri yisumbuye yayize muri Lycee Notre Damme de Cieaux akomereza muri Saint Andre aho yize imibare n'ubugenge (sciences) nyuma yerekeza muri Kaminuza y'u Rwanda aho yize ubuvuzi.<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/91553/menya-byinshi-kuri-dr-claire-karekezi-umunyarwandakazi-wa-mbere-ndetse-rukumbi-ubaga-ubwon-91553.html</ref><ref>http://www.kigaliwomen.com/spip.php?article799</ref>  Dr Karekezi Claire arangije kaminuza i Butare yahisemo kujya kongera ubumenyi mu ishami ryo kubaga [[ubwonko]] n'umugongo akaba yarakoreye imenyerezwa muri [[Suwede|Suweden]],<ref>https://www.jeuneafrique.com/665173/societe/claire-karekezi-la-premiere-neurochirurgienne-du-rwanda/</ref> ariko akomeza kwiga kwimenyereza kubaga [[ubwonko]]. nyuma akomereza imenyerezamwuga mu [https://www.ox.ac.uk/ Kaminuza ya Oxford] mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]], nyuma akomereza amaso ye muri Maroco ahiga imyaka 5, muri 2007 yagiye kwiga andi maso muri [[Kanada|Canada]] mukubaga ibibyimba by'[[ubwonko]]. Akaba yaragiye kwiga kubaga [[ubwonko]] nk'indoto yari afite. Avuga neza [[Ikinyarwanda]], [[Icyongereza]],[[Igiswahili]] n'[[Icyarabu]] gike.

== Umwuga ==
Dr Karekezi Claire ubu akaba ari umuganga mubitaro bya Gisirikare bya kanombe mumujyi wa [[Kigali]] aho abaga [[ubwonko]] ndetse akanavura indwara zibasirwa n'imitsi.<ref>https://acreol.org/team/board-member/</ref>

== Ibihembo ==
Numwe mu bagore bahembwe na Forbes nk'umugore w'intangarugero. Igihembo cyizwi nka Academic Excellence Award gihabwa umugore wabaye indashyikirwa mubijyanye n'amasomo ndetse n'ubumenyi, Uretse kuba umuganga m'u [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] uyu mugore ni umuyobozi mukuru w'ihuriro ry'abagore bo muri [[Afurika]] b'inzobere mukubaga no kuvura [[ubwonko]].<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/dr-karekezi-yegukanye-forbes-woman-africa-awards</ref>

